Use the standard library
This is how to double_the_difference of lst:
  Remember that total is 0
  Do this lst's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of lst's length and 1
    Remember that i is diff of i and total
    Remember that x is item i in lst
    When x is more than 0, then:
      Remember that half is quotient of x and 2
      When product of half and 2 is x, then:
        Do nothing
      But, if not:
        Remember that total is sum of total and product of x and x
      End when
    But, if not:
      Do nothing
    End when
  End do
  The answer is product of total and 2
